<template>
  <v-container fluid class="down-top-padding">
    <BaseBreadcrumb :title="page.title" :icon="page.icon" :breadcrumbs="breadcrumbs"></BaseBreadcrumb>
    <v-row>
      <v-col cols="12" sm="12">
        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Dense">
          <AppbarDence></AppbarDence>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Prominent w/ scroll shrink">
          <AppbarProminentShrink></AppbarProminentShrink>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Prominent w/ scroll shrink and image">
          <AppbarProminentShrinkImage></AppbarProminentShrinkImage>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Hiding on scroll">
          <AppbarHidingScroll></AppbarHidingScroll>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Collapsible bars">
          <AppbarCollpsibleBar></AppbarCollpsibleBar>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Elevate bar on scroll">
          <AppbarElevateBar></AppbarElevateBar>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Inverted scrolling">
          <AppbarInvertedScroll></AppbarInvertedScroll>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Toggle Navigation Drawers">
          <AppbarToggleNavigation></AppbarToggleNavigation>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Scroll threshold">
          <AppbarScrollThreshold></AppbarScrollThreshold>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - Prominent w/ scroll shrink and image, fading on scroll">
          <AppbarShrinkFadeonScroll></AppbarShrinkFadeonScroll>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Appbar - With menu">
          <AppbarwithMenu></AppbarwithMenu>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Appbar",

  data: () => ({
    page: {
      title: "Appbar"
    },
    breadcrumbs: [
      {
        text: "UI Components",
        disabled: false,
        to: "#"
      },
      {
        text: "Appbar",
        disabled: true
      }
    ]
  }),
  components: {
    AppbarCollpsibleBar: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarCollpsibleBar"),
    AppbarDence: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarDence"),
    AppbarElevateBar: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarElevateBar"),
    AppbarHidingScroll: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarHidingScroll"),
    AppbarInvertedScroll: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarInvertedScroll"),
    AppbarProminentShrink: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarProminentShrink"),
    AppbarProminentShrinkImage: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarProminentShrinkImage"
      ),
    AppbarScrollThreshold: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarScrollThreshold"),
    AppbarShrinkFadeonScroll: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarShrinkFadeonScroll"),
    AppbarToggleNavigation: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarToggleNavigation"),
    AppbarwithMenu: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/appbar/AppbarwithMenu")
  }
};
</script>
